ForgeWeapons is the folder you put into the datapacks folder, not the zip.
The forge and hammer are made in the crafting table, not the forge.
Swap bronze ingots in the images for either steel or iron for the weapons. Tools and armor are crafted as normal, all must be centered however.
Iron shield recipe is as normal, but all other shields require reinforced wood in the forge.
Blocks are crafted as expected; they are not placable and only exist for making alloys.
All dusts used in recipes can be collected from geodes, which spawn at y-level 40 and lower, as well as from chest loot.
If playing multiplayer - do NOT fight the ender dragon until all players are ready, as the world difficulty will increase upon its defeat.
Do not lose your TARDIS key. You will only ever get one.
upon loading a new world type /reload

